content: Hello everyone and welcome to the Climate Announcements channel!
Sign up for our phone banks to hear from great speakers and then go persuade key voters together!

@everyone Good morning climate voters! Our Climate Voters for Harris-Walz phonebank will be joined by Washington Lieutenant Governor Danny Heck TONIGHT at 6pm PST/9pm EST. Come hear from a climate champion before making calls to battleground state voters to talk about how this election is crucial to protecting both people and planet. Hope to see you there! RSVP here: https://events.democrats.org/event/677302/?referring_vol=7249094&share_context=dashboard-event-details&sharer_role=SharerRole.ORGANIZER
